2026-07-05 | v1.0.0 | feat: add tooling-pipeline-invalid-jobrequest skill | Documented anti-pattern: JobRequest(None, ...) with type:ignore violates contract, causes coordinator crash. Replacement patterns: use real Job objects (GitJob/AgentJob), or return StageOutcome with RETRY/Continue/FINISH_*. Verified on ProjectHephaestus pipeline #1816 where 5+ JobRequest(None) calls were fixed, 479 unit tests passing.
